    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span>[2 tsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong> to the cooked parsnips and carrots</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mash until smooth – this is your <strong>root veg mash</strong></p>",
