      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>cooked chicken </strong>finely on a clean board and serve it over the <strong>Dijonnaise sauce</strong> with the<strong> root veg mash</strong> and <strong>spring greens</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
